## 5. е…ій”®жҠҖжңҜе®һзҺ°

### 5.1 йЎ№зӣ®жү«жҸҸ

**дҪҝз”ЁJavaParserеә“**пјҡ
```java
public class ProjectScanner {

    public List<CompilationUnit> scanProject(String projectPath) {
        List<CompilationUnit> units = new ArrayList<>();

        // й…ҚзҪ®JavaParser
        ParserConfiguration config = new ParserConfiguration();
        config.setLanguageLevel(ParserConfiguration.LanguageLevel.JAVA_17);

        // жү«жҸҸsrc/main/javaзӣ®еҪ•
        Path sourcePath = Paths.get(projectPath, "src/main/java");

        try (Stream<Path> paths = Files.walk(sourcePath)) {
            paths.filter(p -> p.toString().endsWith(".java"))
                 .forEach(path -> {
                     try {
                         CompilationUnit cu = StaticJavaParser.parse(path);
                         units.add(cu);
                     } catch (IOException e) {
                         logger.warn("Failed to parse: {}", path, e);
                     }
                 });
        }

        return units;
    }
}
```

### 5.2 APIе…ғж•°жҚ®жҸҗеҸ–

**и®ҝй—®иҖ…жЁЎејҸйҒҚеҺҶAST**пјҡ
```java
public class ApiMetadataExtractor extends VoidVisitorAdapter<List<ApiMetadata>> {

    @Override
    public void visit(ClassOrInterfaceDeclaration clazz, List<ApiMetadata> collector) {
        // еҸӘеӨ„зҗҶpublicзұ»
        if (!clazz.isPublic()) {
            return;
        }

        String className = clazz.getNameAsString();
        String packageName = getPackageName(clazz);

        // йҒҚеҺҶжүҖжңүpublicж–№жі•
        clazz.getMethods().stream()
             .filter(MethodDeclaration::isPublic)
             .forEach(method -> {
                 ApiMetadata api = extractMethodMetadata(
                     packageName, className, method
                 );
                 collector.add(api);
             });

        super.visit(clazz, collector);
    }

    private ApiMetadata extractMethodMetadata(
        String packageName, String className, MethodDeclaration method) {

        ApiMetadata api = new ApiMetadata();
        api.setPackageName(packageName);
        api.setClassName(className);
        api.setMethodName(method.getNameAsString());
        api.setSignature(method.getSignature().asString());
        api.setReturnType(method.getType().asString());

        // жҸҗеҸ–еҸӮж•°
        List<Parameter> params = method.getParameters().stream()
            .map(this::extractParameter)
            .collect(Collectors.toList());
        api.setParameters(params);

        // жҸҗеҸ–ејӮеёё
        List<String> exceptions = method.getThrownExceptions().stream()
            .map(ReferenceType::asString)
            .collect(Collectors.toList());
        api.setExceptions(exceptions);

        // жҸҗеҸ–Javadoc
        method.getJavadoc().ifPresent(javadoc -> {
            api.setJavadoc(javadoc.getDescription().toText());
        });

        return api;
    }
}
```

### 5.3 жҸҸиҝ°ж–Үжң¬з”ҹжҲҗ

**зӯ–з•Ҙ**пјҡз»„еҗҲеӨҡз§ҚдҝЎжҒҜз”ҹжҲҗиҜӯд№үдё°еҜҢзҡ„жҸҸиҝ°

```java
public class DescriptionGenerator {

    public String generate(ApiMetadata api) {
        StringBuilder desc = new StringBuilder();

        // 1. зұ»еҗҚе’Ңж–№жі•еҗҚ
        desc.append(api.getClassName())
            .append("зұ»зҡ„")
            .append(api.getMethodName())
            .append("ж–№жі•");

        // 2. Javadocж‘ҳиҰҒ
        if (api.getJavadoc() != null) {
            String summary = extractSummary(api.getJavadoc());
            desc.append("пјҡ").append(summary);
        }

        // 3. еҸӮж•°дҝЎжҒҜ
        if (!api.getParameters().isEmpty()) {
            desc.append("гҖӮжҺҘж”¶еҸӮж•°пјҡ");
            api.getParameters().forEach(param -> {
                desc.append(param.getName())
                    .append("(").append(param.getType()).append(")");
                if (param.getDescription() != null) {
                    desc.append(param.getDescription());
                }
                desc.append("пјҢ");
            });
            desc.setLength(desc.length() - 1); // з§»йҷӨжңҖеҗҺзҡ„йҖ—еҸ·
        }

        // 4. иҝ”еӣһзұ»еһӢ
        desc.append("гҖӮиҝ”еӣһпјҡ")
            .append(api.getReturnType());

        // 5. ејӮеёёдҝЎжҒҜ
        if (!api.getExceptions().isEmpty()) {
            desc.append("гҖӮеҸҜиғҪжҠӣеҮәпјҡ")
                .append(String.join("гҖҒ", api.getExceptions()));
        }

        // 6. дҫқиө–дҝЎжҒҜ
        if (!api.getDependencies().isEmpty()) {
            desc.append("гҖӮдҫқиө–пјҡ")
                .append(String.join("гҖҒ", api.getDependencies()));
        }

        return desc.toString();
    }

    private String extractSummary(String javadoc) {
        // жҸҗеҸ–з¬¬дёҖеҸҘиҜқдҪңдёәж‘ҳиҰҒ
        int dotIndex = javadoc.indexOf('гҖӮ');
        if (dotIndex == -1) {
            dotIndex = javadoc.indexOf('.');
        }
        return dotIndex > 0 ? javadoc.substring(0, dotIndex) : javadoc;
    }
}
```

### 5.4 еҗ‘йҮҸзҙўеј•жһ„е»ә

**дҪҝз”ЁFAISS**пјҡ
```java
public class VectorIndexBuilder {

    private final EmbeddingService embeddingService;
    private final int dimension;

    public VectorIndex build(List<ApiMetadata> apis) {
        // 1. жү№йҮҸз”ҹжҲҗеҗ‘йҮҸ
        List<String> descriptions = apis.stream()
            .map(ApiMetadata::getDescription)
            .collect(Collectors.toList());

        List<float[]> vectors = embeddingService.embedBatch(descriptions);

        // 2. жһ„е»әFAISSзҙўеј•
        // дҪҝз”ЁIndexFlatIPпјҲеҶ…з§ҜпјүжҲ–IndexFlatL2пјҲж¬§ж°Ҹи·қзҰ»пјү
        // иҝҷйҮҢдҪҝз”ЁеҶ…з§ҜпјҢйҖӮеҗҲеҪ’дёҖеҢ–зҡ„еҗ‘йҮҸ
        swigfaiss.IndexFlatIP index = new swigfaiss.IndexFlatIP(dimension);

        // 3. ж·»еҠ еҗ‘йҮҸ
        for (int i = 0; i < vectors.size(); i++) {
            index.add(vectors.get(i));
            apis.get(i).setVector(vectors.get(i));
        }

        return new VectorIndex(index, apis);
    }
}
```

### 5.5 иҜӯд№үжЈҖзҙўе®һзҺ°

```java
public class SemanticRetriever {

    private final VectorIndex index;
    private final EmbeddingService embeddingService;
    private final MetadataStore metadataStore;

    public List<ApiMetadata> search(String query, int topK) {
        // 1. жҹҘиҜўеҗ‘йҮҸеҢ–
        float[] queryVector = embeddingService.embed(query);

        // 2. еҗ‘йҮҸжЈҖзҙў
        SearchResult result = index.search(queryVector, topK);

        // 3. еҠ иҪҪе…ғж•°жҚ®
        List<ApiMetadata> apis = new ArrayList<>();
        for (int i = 0; i < result.getIds().length; i++) {
            String apiId = result.getIds()[i];
            float score = result.getScores()[i];

            ApiMetadata api = metadataStore.get(apiId);
            api.setScore(score);
            apis.add(api);
        }

        return apis;
    }
}
```

