### 13.8 еӨ–йғЁAPIжҸҸиҝ°з”ҹжҲҗ

**жү©еұ•DescriptionGenerator**пјҡ
```java
public class DescriptionGenerator {
    
    public String generate(ApiMetadata api) {
        if (api.getSourceType() == DocumentSourceType.INTERNAL_CODE) {
            return generateInternalDescription(api);
        } else {
            return generateExternalDescription(api);
        }
    }
    
    private String generateExternalDescription(ApiMetadata api) {
        StringBuilder desc = new StringBuilder();
        
        // 1. жңҚеҠЎеҗҚе’Ңз«ҜзӮ№
        if (api.getExternalInfo() != null) {
            desc.append(api.getExternalInfo().getServiceName()).append("жңҚеҠЎзҡ„");
        }
        if (api.getHttpMethod() != null) {
            desc.append(api.getHttpMethod()).append(" ");
        }
        if (api.getEndpoint() != null) {
            desc.append(api.getEndpoint()).append("жҺҘеҸЈ");
        }
        
        // 2. жҸҸиҝ°
        if (api.getDescription() != null) {
            desc.append("пјҡ").append(api.getDescription());
        }
        
        // 3. еҸӮж•°
        if (!api.getParameters().isEmpty()) {
            desc.append("гҖӮиҜ·жұӮеҸӮж•°пјҡ");
            api.getParameters().forEach(param -> {
                desc.append(param.getName())
                    .append("(").append(param.getType()).append(")пјҢ");
            });
            desc.setLength(desc.length() - 1);
        }
        
        // 4. иҜ·жұӮ/е“Қеә”дҪ“
        if (api.getRequestBody() != null) {
            desc.append("гҖӮиҜ·жұӮдҪ“пјҡ").append(api.getRequestBody());
        }
        if (api.getResponseBody() != null) {
            desc.append("гҖӮе“Қеә”пјҡ").append(api.getResponseBody());
        }
        
        return desc.toString();
    }
}
```

### 13.9 иҮӘеҠЁжӣҙж–°зӯ–з•Ҙ

**ж–ҮжЎЈеҲ·ж–°и°ғеәҰеҷЁ**пјҡ
```java
public class DocumentRefreshScheduler {
    
    private final ScheduledExecutorService scheduler;
    private final DocumentSourceManager sourceManager;
    
    public void start() {
        // жҜҸ5еҲҶй’ҹжЈҖжҹҘдёҖж¬Ўжӣҙж–°
        scheduler.scheduleAtFixedRate(() -> {
            List<DocumentSource> sources = loadAllSources();
            
            for (DocumentSource source : sources) {
                if (source.isEnabled() && shouldRefresh(source)) {
                    try {
                        sourceManager.updateSource(source.getId());
                        logger.info("Refreshed: {}", source.getName());
                    } catch (Exception e) {
                        logger.error("Failed to refresh: {}", source.getName(), e);
                    }
                }
            }
        }, 0, 5, TimeUnit.MINUTES);
    }
    
    private boolean shouldRefresh(DocumentSource source) {
        if (source.getLastIndexed() == null) return true;
        
        long elapsed = Duration.between(
            source.getLastIndexed(), 
            LocalDateTime.now()
        ).getSeconds();
        
        return elapsed >= source.getRefreshInterval();
    }
}
```

### 13.10 е®Ңж•ҙе®һзҺ°жөҒзЁӢ

**еҲқе§Ӣзҙўеј•жһ„е»ә**пјҡ
